headline: Option Volatility And Earnings Report For January 20 - 23
summary: Earnings season ramps up this week with some big names set to report. This week we have Netflix, Intel, Johnson & Johnson, Freeport McMoran and 3M Company all reporting in what shapes as a busy and pivotal week for stocks.
